verbose_text: It is a complex lipid of glycerides, free fatty acids, phospholipids, sterols, sterol esters, fat-soluble vitamins, tocopherol, carbonyls, hydrocarbons, carotenoids, small amounts of charred casein, traces of minerals like calcium, phosphorus, iron, copper etc. Ayurveda describes that ' Ghrita ', is a useful adjuvant / vehicle.
